### Non-SSE request
POST http://localhost:4321/api/ai/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{SUPABASE_JWT}}

{
  "source_text": "{{LONG_SOURCE_TEXT_1000_CHARS}}",
  "max_proposals": 12
}

### SSE request
POST http://localhost:4321/api/ai/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{SUPABASE_JWT}}

{
  "source_text": "{{LONG_SOURCE_TEXT_1000_CHARS}}",
  "max_proposals": 10
}

### 401 (no auth)
POST http://localhost:4321/api/ai/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source_text": "{{LONG_SOURCE_TEXT_1000_CHARS}}",
  "max_proposals": 10
}

### 415 (wrong content-type)
POST http://localhost:4321/api/ai/generate
Content-Type: text/plain
Authorization: Bearer {{SUPABASE_JWT}}

{
  "source_text": "{{LONG_SOURCE_TEXT_1000_CHARS}}",
  "max_proposals": 10
}

### 422 (invalid body)
POST http://localhost:4321/api/ai/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{SUPABASE_JWT}}

{
  "source_text": "too short",
  "max_proposals": 100
}


